      "name": "CPB hemolysis applicability domain",
      "description": "Model is applicable to adult CPB procedures with pump flow rates between 3.0 and 6.0 L/min and impeller speeds between 2000 and 3500 RPM. Applicability is restricted to the FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry; results are not transferable to axial-flow or pulsatile-flow devices. Blood hematocrit assumed in the range 30–45%."
    },
